## ChickenSwipe

A simple game made using Unity3D and C#. The game detects the system it is running on to determine whether to use touch input or keyboard input. The project can be run on iOS, Android, Windows, and Mac OS after building it within Unity3D.

Features of the game include:

- Collectible coins
- Skin customization
- Touch or keyboard input
- Arena customization
- Purchasing skins with in-game currency
- Non-intrusive adverts using Google Admob
